reviewText: Kyoko loses her baby boy in a car accident, a little after that she becomes a wet nurse. for those who don't know what a wet nurse is they are women who breast feed other peoples children. years later two of the boys that Kyoko was a wet nurse to reconnect with her in a motherly/ romantic relationship. Kyoko's daughter Marika even falls in love with the boy named Toji. but in the end Kyoko kills all of them nd barring them in the back yard.

Disturbing adult anime, where's part 3? We are left with a cliffhanger in which the 2 detectives are investigating Kyoko's front yard. Would've also liked to see what happens when they find the bodies and what will be of Kyoko's fate. Oh well we will never know.
Was worth it and I enjoyed it.
It is all you expect from a really good hentai movie. The animation is drawn really well and you feel like bondage this is definitely one that you'd like to watch
